{"tid":1899240,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[再開]貓貓需要A型血","createTime":"2020-02-26T13:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T23:08:25.000Z","uid":219969,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"d0ed1fbf1275115c8667e59628d8b23923ea1b7d","tid":1899240,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:03:46.000Z","msg":"上一個post：<br />\n我隻貓一個月前check出cancer，最近開始出現不吃不喝嘅情況<br />\n今日睇醫生話有嚴重貧血、敗血同其他問題，有生命危險，急需A型貓血<br />\n因為已經問哂啲朋友，又入哂好多fb 貓group問，都冇啱嘅貓血，醫院淨係得包唔適用嘅血，如果冇都要照用住先⋯⋯<br />\n實在冇哂辦法，所以上嚟開post，如果你隻貓貓係A型血可以捐，或者唔知血型但有意嘅都請聯絡我<br />\nTg: Penguinnhoker<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位嘅幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驗完血之後發現全部都唔得<br />\n依家用緊血庫入面比較match嘅血<br />\n但係都有較高嘅風險<br />\n所以想問有冇其他貓貓願意幫下佢stand by<br />\n今晚12點之後要絕食<br />\n聽朝醫院10點左右會通知我仲需唔需要揾貓捐血<br />\n如果要架話我再通知願意幫手嘅貓(人)?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n捐血條件及程序：<br />\n-年齡介乎1-6歲<br />\n-4公斤以上最佳<br />\n-健康<br />\n-定期打傳染病預防針（最好每年都有打，齊針）<br />\n-10-14天內無預防針注射<br />\n-近期無服用任何藥物（腸內寄生蟲杜蟲藥、心絲蟲預防藥及體外寄生蟲預防藥除外）<br />\n-無接受輸血紀錄<br />\n-近期無懷孕及分娩<br />\n-需要空腹8小時<br />\n-A型血（多數唐貓都係A型）如果唔知血型但符合條件又可以捐都可以contact我<br />\n<br />\n捐血程序：<br />\n如果貓貓符合條件可以捐血(感謝！)，請tg <a href=\"https://t.me/Penguinnhoker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FPenguinnhoker&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=5dd99116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Penguinnhoker</a><br />\n確定捐血時間後，再去旺角麥花臣診所驗血，醫生確認ok就可以捐<br />\n唔該哂，再一次感激！！！"},{"pid":"9c56aca187fc2c962fb003c20fbeac4b79db2cae","tid":1899240,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"$20"},{"pid":"91a6efe07a2bfa1055aaa5924667299fcf208ed7","tid":1899240,"uid":219969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DhTjabL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDhTjabL.jpg&h=e6df7b00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCFYqK7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCFYqK7.jpg&h=01d6f049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfEZabP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrfEZabP.jpg&h=dbeeb659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxmQgRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcxmQgRQ.jpg&h=bc2b5b60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b425e284bcfc461e4e09c6ad5704594f492d264","tid":1899240,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:07:44.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413a09fb52cc03b5e64b07858dd99383cafdc856","tid":1899240,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:09:06.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"50a4272ffa2cd77341f9c95acf440bad4dff5abc","tid":1899240,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:09:10.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9abf21c665cee781e5f64cb61f7e19ce22ecd4dc","tid":1899240,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:09:34.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"02d862231dd14cf6def8f6848ee31a32ed3c101c","tid":1899240,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T13:11:02.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frow